<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2><span>著作信息</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>安布罗斯餐厅Zeta-01分店</strong><br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xiaoyoued" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5857031); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5857031&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781488" alt="xiaoyoued" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5857031)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xiaoyoued" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5857031); return false;">xiaoyoued</a></span><br />
新人第一作，基于<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/shadow-milkyway-hub">晦暗星河</a>设定的安布罗斯餐厅GOI格式</p>
<hr />
<p>图片来源：本人于傍晚时分的学校拍摄，遵守CC-BY-SA 3.0</p>
<hr />
<p>特别感谢：为菜品设计提出许多点子的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/orange-gummy-cat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5929325); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5929325&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781488" alt="orange-gummy-cat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5929325)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/orange-gummy-cat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5929325); return false;">orange-gummy-cat</a></span><br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/feitag" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4357011); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4357011&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781488" alt="feitag" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4357011)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/feitag" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4357011); return false;">feitag</a></span>大佬的<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/how-to-modify-the-css-of-ambrose-goi-format">安布罗斯餐厅GOI格式代码指南</a>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fuban" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2922576); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2922576&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781488" alt="fuban" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2922576)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fuban" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2922576); return false;">fuban</a></span>的<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/module-guide">迭代指导</a>与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4055881&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781488" alt="Etinjat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4055881)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;">Etinjat</a></span>的<a href="http://scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-sss">迭代示例</a>，完全不懂代码的我学到许多</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+55</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
